OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet and windy start to the
OL,6,Fmorning, with rain clearing
OL,7,Fnorthwards. Soon brightening up with a
OL,8,Fmixture of sunshine and showers, some
OL,9,Fheavy with the risk of thunder.
OL,10,FPotentially merging to give some
OL,11,Flonger downpours later. Feeling rather
OL,12,Fhumid.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FHeavy showers will clear
OL,15,Feastwards during the evening. Mostly
OL,16,Fdry overnight, with clear spells.
OL,17,FHowever, a few light showers remain
OL,18,Fpossible. Staying breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
