OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA bright morning, with spells
OL,6,Fof sunshine. An increasing risk of
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks of rain developing
OL,8,Fas the afternoon progresses, turning
OL,9,Fheavy over the hills by the evening.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FStaying unsettled, with a mixture of
OL,14,Fsunny spells and showery rain. Some of
OL,15,Fthe showers could be heavy and
OL,16,Fthundery. Temperatures a little below
OL,17,Fnormal, with some chilly nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
